[name]
ISO-8859-1 encoding

[input]
=encoding iso-8859-1

=head1 ACCENTS

Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!!

    Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
      Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!
        Beyoncé!  Beyoncé!

Older versions didn't convert Beyoncé in verbatim.

[output]
.SH "ACCENTS"
.IX Header "ACCENTS"
Beyonce\*'!  Beyonce\*'!  Beyonce\*'!!
.PP
.Vb 3
\&    Beyonce\*'!  Beyonce\*'!
\&      Beyonce\*'!  Beyonce\*'!
\&        Beyonce\*'!  Beyonce\*'!
.Ve
.PP
Older versions didn't convert Beyonce\*' in verbatim.
